milestones.description: Martin Suji has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for KENYA, going past Aasif Karim's 1
Hitesh Modi and Sandeep Gupta's 34-run partnership is KENYA's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 21 between Tito Odumbe and David Tikolo
Hitesh Modi and Aasif Karim's 89-run partnership is KENYA's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 29 between Hitesh Modi and Aasif Karim
Tito Odumbe has broken the record for most catches (4) in ODIs for KENYA, going past Hitesh Modi's 3
Rajab Ali has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (7) for KENYA, going past Chudasama
This is the lowest match aggregate (378) involving teams Sri Lanka & Kenya in ODIs
